# The old serverless backend (scrypt auth + Stripe) is superseded by the
# browser -> Neon (Data API + Neon Auth) architecture. Kept in the repo for
# history, but NOT deployed. The deployed app is just index.html.
#
# Every pattern is ROOT-ANCHORED (leading /) so it only matches top-level paths
# and never reaches into .git internals (an unanchored "db" previously matched
# .git/objects/db/* and corrupted the build checkout).
/api
/vercel.json
/package.json
/package-lock.json
/db
/.env.example
/BACKEND.md
/NEON-REBUILD.md
/README.md
